The ["Davis Police Department"] issues a lot of ["Noise Violation" Noise Violations]. This has created a large amount of animosity between students and the police. Many officers have become famous or shall we say infamous in their dealings with ["Noise Violation" offenders]. This is a place to share your stories. It doesn't matter whether you are positive or negative. Just try to remain as factual as possible. The Noise Police are not to be confused with the ["Gay PD"].
